<br />
<br />The real issue is that I"m still a little fuzzy on how 8x16 sprites are accessed.  If there is bit to indicate whether or not the tile is located at $0000 or $1000, why do reference documents say that one tile is always at $0000 and it's associated lower tile is always at $1000?  If that's always true, what's the purpose of the bit?

		

